        "timestamp": "2017-09-28 13:44:36.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nI really like where this change is trying to go, but it breaks something pretty key along they way.\nIn the kubernetes simpledemo.json file you have here: https://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/16119\nthe namespace is hardcoded to onap.  OOM has the ability to use different namespaces and currently it uses \"sed\" to swap out \".onap-\" with the user's desired namespace.  We will have to think of another way to have both this change and the ability to use namespaces other than \"onap\"",
        "patchset_number": 1
